thread.title: Disney Reportedly in Talks to Purchase 21st Century Fox
thread.title_full: /co/ - Disney Reportedly in Talks to Purchase 21st Century Fox - Comics & Cartoons - 4chan

posts.author: Anonymous
posts.text:
>>96579452
Fox apparently wants to spin off their entertainment properties and has since their attempt to buy Time-Warner collapsed. Losing Star Wars to Disney was a pretty big blow to them since a lot of their big film franchises have pretty much reached the point of diminishing returns.
Meanwhile Disney wants to launch a stream service that will compete with existing ones so they need a larger library of films and shows; Fox also has quite a few properties that Disney could easily exploit and outright needs in the case of A New Hope. Even the stuff like X-Men that isn't really working for Fox anymore might well be revitalized if they could connect it to the MCU; look at what doing that did for the Spider-Man franchise. Homecoming is the most successful Spider-Man film since 3 and wound up surpassing GotG 2 and Wonder Woman worldwide.
Their other best option would have been Time-Warner since that gives them the WB, MGM, and Hanna-Barbera libraries but AT&T is already moving on that.
Talks might have stalled but such a deal makes too much sense for both sides for them to be dead forever. That would take somebody else buying Fox's entertainment division first.

Felipe responde acusão de Euriquinho: “Meu caráter é uma herança” por Carlos Antônio Mello Publicado às 07:26 de 07/11/17 leituras Euriquinho cedeu entrevista coletiva na tarde de segunda-feira (06), o dirigente acusou o ex-jogador, Felipe, de boicote. Segundo o vice de futebol do Vasco, o ex-atleta fazia ligações para os jogadores. Com isso, Felipe sentiu-se ofendido e respondeu. 
FALA DO VICE DE FUTEBOL DO VASCO: 
“No futebol acabamos sabendo de tudo. Muitos atletas receberam ligações, outros se reuniram. Os que estavam vindo receberam ligações para não virem. O ex-atleta que fez isso é o Felipe (que está na chapa do candidato Julio Brant).” 
Não demorou muito para Felipe responder o comentário feito por Euriquinho. 
RESPOSTA DE FELIPE: 
“Minha vitoriosa carreira no Vasco foi conquistada com muito trabalho e dedicação. Meu caráter é uma herança de minha família e da minha formação como atleta nas divisões de base do Vasco. Minha imagem é o meu maior patrimônio, como ex atleta, ídolo, profissional do futebol e pai de família. Os inúmeros títulos que conquistei no Vasco são o meu orgulho. Portanto, repudio, veementemente, as declarações FALSAS que essas pessoas insistem em utilizar para tumultuar o processo eleitoral do Vasco a partir do momento que me posiciono a favor da renovação e da transparência.Também não é novidade esse tipo de ataque, afinal é uma tática comum que usam em épocas de eleição. A minha história é a certeza que esses comentários maldosos e sem credibilidade não refletem a verdade. Por fim, peço para que o vascaíno reflita e veja que tentam engana-lo ao colocar a culpa na mentira. Não assumir a responsabilidade é a arma da incompetência. 
Saudações Vascaínas.”

posts.text:
By Michelle Young 

Eating is a basic human instinct. To some it is a chore. Individuals with fine tastes usually consider eating as a lifestyle. They view it as an experience that has to be savored from the beginning to the end. Such individuals are in love with the best Caribbean food Pasadena . That is because they know that it is one of the best delicacies that money can buy. There are mediocre meals then there are those that are exceptional in all respects. Actually, mediocrity is one of the worst words in the English language. One should not eat averagely.

There are a number of Caribbean islands. They include Turks & Caicos, Barbados, Bahamas, the Dominican Republic, Cuba, Grenada, Jamaica, and Haiti among others. These islands are known for having some of the best delicacies in the world. These nations are great tourist destinations. Every year, millions of people from different parts of the world usually visit the Turks & Caicos Islands.

One of the common local delicacies is seafood. There are different types of seafood. The good thing about seafood is that it is not only delicious. It is also loaded with valuable nutrients. It is rich in proteins, carbohydrates and minerals. Proteins are the building blocks of muscle. They also form the blood and other essential bodily fluids.

There are many things that one will enjoy when visiting the Dominican Republic. Of course, the idyllic beaches are enchanting. One will also love the local people. They are usually very friendly. Another thing that one will enjoy is roast pork. This is a special type of pork that has a very inviting aroma, a great appearance, and an amazing taste.

Caribbean dishes have a solid reputation. They are loved by people from different parts of the world. One can find a local restaurant that serves these dishes. Finding the right restaurant will be the biggest challenge. Not every restaurant is reputable. As a matter of fact, some are known for having bad customer service. There are many great restaurants.

To know whether or not a restaurant is reputable, there will be need to carry out internet research. The World Wide Web is the best source of information. One needs to visit internet review websites that have reviews of restaurants. A good facility will have five star ratings and amazing reviews. The opinions of the past customers of a cafe should not be taken for granted.

If possible, one should also visit the website of a service provider. A top restaurant will have a professional website. Apart from reading online information, there is need to consult family members, friends, and work colleagues who are in love with exotic delicacies. Some of them might actually offer one with valuable referrals. One should search for high quality information.

Humans need to eat to survive. Eating should be an experience. One should enjoy everything about the eating process. The most important quality of a meal is the taste. The others are smell and meal appearance. Human beings are visual beings. Thus, they usually judge meals based on how they look. A meal is as good as how it is prepared.

posts.text:
Názory & komentáre Futbalisti SR do 23 rokov postúpili vo finále Challenge Trophy Zverenci Pavla Hapala uspeli pred dvoma rokmi vo finále nad Tureckom v jedenástkovom rozstrele a majú šancu stať sa prvým tímom s dvoma celkovými víťazstvami za sebou. 0 1 
Žiar nad Hronom   Slovenskí futbalisti do 23 rokov budú v stredu obhajovať prvenstvo v International Challenge Trophy. V Žiari nad Hronom nastúpia o 17.00 h proti Anglicku C, ktoré už v tejto edícii dlhodobého prípravného turnaja zdolali na jeho pôde 4:3. Zverenci Pavla Hapala uspeli pred dvoma rokmi vo finále nad Tureckom v jedenástkovom rozstrele a majú šancu stať sa prvým tímom s dvoma celkovými víťazstvami za sebou. 
Slováci triumfovali v Anglicku 4:3, hoci prehrávali 1:3. „Angličania omladili svoj tím v porovnaní s predchádzajúcim zápasom, čo sme odohrali u nich. Určite budú veľmi tvrdí v súbojoch. Budeme sa snažiť hrať svoju hru a predviesť divákom atraktívny a dobrý futbal. Samozrejme, zabojujeme o víťazstvo, ktoré obhajujeme z minulého ročníka Challenge Trophy,“ povedal tréner Hapal na oficiálnej stránke Slovenského futbalového zväzu (SFZ). 
Turnaj je určený pre poloprofesionálne mládežnícke výbery do 23 rokov. Premiérovo sa uskutočnil v rokoch 2005 až 2006 za účasti štyroch tímov bez finálového stretnutia. V nasledujúcich troch edíciách súťaže sa stali celkovými víťazmi Belgicko (2007 – 2009), Portugalsko (2009 – 2011) a Turecko (2011 – 2013). Slovensko to dokázalo v rokoch 2013 až 2015. Hapal absolvoval prvý duel po nástupe na lavičku reprezentácie do 21 rokov práve v semifinále Challenge Trophy 26. marca 2015 v Myjave proti Nórsku. 
V Žiari nad Hronom sa sčasti obnoví spolupráca z predchádzajúceho cyklu dvadsaťjednotiek, v ktorom sa Slovensko prebojovalo na záverečný turnaj majstrovstiev Európy v Poľsku. Vo výbere sa opäť stretli Ľubomír Šatka, Martin Valjent, Branislav Niňaj, Martin Chrien či Pavol Šafranko. Viacerí zasiahli aj do prípravného súboja s Anglickom C. „Tie pocity, opäť vidieť chlapcov, boli naozaj pekné. Veď sme sa dlhšie nevideli,“ uviedol Hapal. „Je to skvelý pocit, byť opäť v tomto tíme. A týka sa to aj celého realizačného tímu. V bývalej dvadsaťjednotke sme tvorili naozaj vynikajúcu partiu a preto som sa veľmi tešil, keď mi tréner Pavel Hapal zavolal a povolal ma do mužstva, ktoré sa predstaví vo finále Challenge Trophy. A mám k tomu ešte bonus navyše. Konečne som sa mohol aspoň na pár dní vrátiť domov. Veď do Zvolena, kde máme zraz a do Žiaru nad Hronom, kde budeme hrať, to mám z Banskej Bystrice naozaj na skok,“ dodal Chrien, ktorý prestúpil po ME 2017 do portugalskej Benficy Lisabon. posts.text:
台中市议员赖佳微7日在台中市议会教育文化委员会进行业务质询，针对活化台中一中旧眷舍、单身宿舍，及市内各级学校参与花博及生态教育提出质询，要求权责应活化利用；虽台南、台北也有不同着名文创基地，若能藉由台中在地团队操刀改造，才能突显出台中自己的在地风格。 
赖佳微指出，台中一中有一老旧眷舍，位置邻近一中商圈，面积足有743平方公尺，因学校常年经费不足无法改建活用，已荒废12年之久，内部墙壁斑驳受损严重且堆满垃圾，也屡遭周围居民投诉有治安上的隐忧。另有单身教职员宿舍土地面积250平方公尺，目前建物结构良好，里面仅有一位教职员居住。 
赖佳微表示，北区学校林立，大学有台中科技大学、中国医药学院，高中有台中一中、台中二中、晓明女中、新民高中，国中有双十国中、立人国中、五权国中，实为台中的文化区。 
台中一中、五权国中皆设有美术班，台中科技大学有闻名全国的商业设计系，若能活化两处空间并加入地方学校特色，实为美事一桩；虽台南、台北也有不同着名文创基地，但不同区域有不同的美感特色，若能由台中在地团队操刀改造，才能突显出台中自己的在地风格。 
赖佳微说，教育局如何让学生对于2018的花博盛会有参与感？虽教育局在课程规划中加入石虎保育双语文章，但最重要的是让学生得以在校园中了解大自然之美，对于身边的美好生活环境应该有能力自己创造，进而培养爱护土地、爱护环境的心，让美时时在身边，而不是舍近求远到山里、野溪才找得到美丽的景色。 
(中时)
